5b0","tid":1000655,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁先講下我嘅見解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我估讀faa4<br />\n<a href=\"https://ja.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E8%8F%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fja.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258F%25AF&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMAcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=1e51f43a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ja.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E8%8F%AF</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZOuKkF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZOuKkF.png&h=420fa721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我估個意思應該係第一個はな"},{"pid":"885980fd419cfdb489640866bab07ddd475cd6aa","tid":1000655,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"讀返華<br />\n讀花真係指花，古字，呢到唔適用<br />\n讀話一般都係地名，姓氏"},{"pid":"b5b2c55cd6ed44a6760d64b1097a8bd47322d770","tid":1000655,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"885980fd419cfdb489640866bab07ddd475cd6aa","tid":1000655,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"讀返華<br />\n讀花真係指花，古字，呢到唔適用<br />\n讀話一般都係地名，姓氏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709ec82545f6b8fe17861e4f3ce378de6d10f5f8","tid":1000655,"uid":230820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"正常漢字都有幾個讀法，點讀都係睇情況多<br />\n但正常文章你就咁見到一隻「華」字就通常指「花」，就讀hana。<br />\n用係名字就多數讀ka（華X,X華），意思都係指花。另外名字上帶「花（X花,花X)」都係多數都讀ka，除非係單字一個花就讀番hana<br />\n所以你當華同花基本上係同一樣都可以<br />\nBtw鐵華團係個好好玩既例子，「火」其中一個讀音都係ka，所以鐵華團暗藏鐵火團，鐵花團的意思，係幾浪漫的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}